WEBVTT

00:15:25.674 --> 00:15:31.280
starting with our own cherished
versions of reality.

00:15:33.035 --> 00:15:36.904
Imagine if you let go of fantasies

00:15:36.928 --> 00:15:40.786
of a society purged
of these or those people.

00:15:41.561 --> 00:15:45.214
Imagine if I let go of my habit

00:15:45.755 --> 00:15:48.825
of saving the world behind your back,

00:15:49.833 --> 00:15:51.230
of deliberating on the future

00:15:51.254 --> 00:15:52.729
of your work,

00:15:53.260 --> 00:15:54.506
your food,

00:15:54.530 --> 00:15:56.000
your schools,

00:15:56.024 --> 00:15:59.034
in places where you couldn't
get past security.